{"tid":662320,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人對毒撚格仔裇衫有陰影？","createTime":"2018-05-12T10:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T16:52:29.000Z","uid":24642,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c4034a89dc29b6211fca812f0a292f4662de3828","tid":662320,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"細個呀媽成日買格仔裇我著<br />\n係啲藍色 橙仔 粉紅 細格仔 懶花巧嗰種款<br />\n佢話我著得好好睇<br />\n嗰陣我唔識嘢咪成日著<br />\n<br />\n到大個咗識嘢 就知格仔裇真係好毒<br />\n望返以前著格仔衫影嘅相 真係慘不忍睹<br />\n依家見到格仔衫 會好反感<br />\n唔想再著<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f20cf16fdb2790328acdf4ceca19c533c73c6d","tid":662320,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:31:42.000Z","msg":"大隻著好睇"},{"pid":"559894b98ecff9485162285b63829f6348c7d8b8","tid":662320,"uid":139448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"正太著會可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992d6066e53759f442dc29cd74b2ec3376a58ba5","tid":662320,"uid":82917,"like":51,"dislike":4,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"型撚到震喎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/185949_b6d81756b9c64eefb6f0d85b3c6334a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F185949_b6d81756b9c64eefb6f0d85b3c6334a0.png&h=42c5546b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71584b22519773cb30275c2c770e9d8e0bfdbca2","tid":662320,"uid":27247,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"睇人啦<br />\n木村以前著咪一樣型到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5f7eafe55233a85c6eacb437c036ec25f4d9ba","tid":662320,"uid":20285,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"格仔恤唔會毒<br />\n係個人先會毒"},{"pid":"3a11c315572bc648956ad1336a173438fa587e29","tid":662320,"uid":5668